  "description": "If you are using the SDK in a .NET Core application and make use of either the Microsoft Dependency Injection or Configuration libraries you can use the CheckoutSDK.Extensions.Microsoft package.",
  "source": "@site/docs/net-core.md",
  "permalink": "/checkout-sdk-net/net-core",
  "sidebar": "someSidebar",
